<div id="pf5517" class="pf w59 h359" data-page-no="5517"><div class="pc pc5517 w59 h359"><div class="t m616 x65 h63 y1a9a ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">RAY or the Unread] d,Peop14 Group of Nati </div><div class="t mf6d x12 h63 y1e3b ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eric s in ,,he uppe Yakinia Valley of </div><div class="t m5 xca h63 y1b08 ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m168b x19f h63 y1a6a ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">th </div><div class="t m82b xa4 h63 y1a9c ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ashington where no permane work </div><div class="t mb03 x69 h63 y213c ff1 fs1e fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stablished. </div><div class="t m2f8 x14 h27 y3111 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessed through them (see Gen. 12:3; Gal. 3:8) when they (the Jews) ruled </div><div class="t m1e5 x14 h27 y2f4c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">over the nations. But Paul made it clear that the real promise to Abraham </div><div class="t m650 x14 h27 y2f0a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was not a piece of land or a throne, but righteousness; and Abraham&apos;s real </div><div class="t m1488 x14 h27 y2bf2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">descendants are those who have Abraham&apos;s faith, regardless of their blood </div><div class="t m25b x14 h27 y29e3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">relationship to him. Any person, of any nation, can by faith lay claim to the </div><div class="t m4cc x14 h27 y29ed ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">promise of righteousness that was first made to Abraham. This, Paul said, </div><div class="t m8d4 x14 h27 y2bb4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is how all nations were to be blessed through Abraham. </div><div class="t m30b x14 h87 y245b ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">APPLICATION TO MY LIFE: </div><div class="t m34e x28 h27 y21bd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m1184 x5b h27 y21ba ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How important is it to my peace of mind to know that through </div><div class="t m2 x28 h27 y2332 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus my sins are entirely forgiven? What would life be like if I did </div><div class="t m7ec x28 h27 y21a4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not know that? </div><div class="t m34e x28 h27 y1b59 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m87c x5b h27 y213e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Most Christians today are not blood descendants of Abraham. </div><div class="t m1dc x28 h27 y1b09 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nevertheless, in what ways can we have a false hope of favor with </div><div class="t m2f6 x28 h27 y13d3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God as the chosen nation did in Christ&apos;s time? </div><div class="t m34e x28 h27 y20dc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m74c x5b h27 y1645 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How can I know whether I am truly trusting in Christ or my good </div><div class="t m1367 x28 h27 y1cf5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">deeds for salvation? </div><div class="t m7f2 x5d h87 y1c57 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m1a3 x57 h27 y1a44 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read the chapter titled </div><div class="t m67b x5d h27 y20d7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Justified by Faith&quot; in </div><div class="t m1142 x8b h16 y199b ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selected Messages, </div><div class="t m11d x46 h27 y1d70 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book 1, pp. 389-398. </div><div class="t m8d4 x5d h87 y1cf9 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m109 xb h27 y1b0e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We can be saved only by faith in Christ, never by our </div><div class="t m44c x5d h27 y1e36 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works, by family ties, or by church membership. Faith in Christ brings </div><div class="t m275 x5d h27 y10d1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">both the forgiveness of sin and the power of the Holy Spirit that transforms </div><div class="t m7ec x5d h27 y1d14 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our lives. Abraham&apos;s faith in God&apos;s promises brought him the gift of right-</div><div class="t me4b x5d h27 y1a47 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eousness, and that same gift is available to every Christian who exercises </div><div class="t m1145 x5d h27 y1ff7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Abraham&apos;s faith in God. Christ Himself is the Gift who comes to us by the </div><div class="t m563 x5d h27 y16cd ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit. </div><div class="t mcf x5d h87 y11cc ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
